  ${
    $d F x y $.  $d G a b x y $.  $d H a b x y $.  $d O x y $.  $d X x y $.
    $d Y a b x y $.
    ghgrpi.1 $e |- G e. Grp $.
    ghgrpi.2 $e |- X = ran G $.
    ghgrpi.3 $e |- F : X -onto-> Y $.
    ghgrpi.4 $e |- Y C_ A $.
    ghgrpi.5 $e |- O Fn ( A X. A ) $.
    ghgrpi.6 $e |- ( ( x e. X /\ y e. X ) ->
                     ( F ` ( x G y ) ) = ( ( F ` x ) O ( F ` y ) ) ) $.
    ghgrpi.7 $e |- H = ( O |` ( Y X. Y ) ) $.

